title: NOISY DOVE DISRUPTING MY SLEEP. WILL AVA STEP IN AND HELP CULL?
text:
NOISY DOVE DISRUPTING MY SLEEP. WILL AVA STEP IN AND HELP CULL?   
Dear ASS Advertisement 
It started about two weeks ago, it was once my favorite birdie Spotted Dove Kookoo every early morning at 7am plus, very loudly, affected my sleep waken me up and unable to continue sleeping since it's so early. 
Now I beginning to unlike such kinda birdie as it's a noise nuisance to me now. I had even complained to AVA, a week ago but they Bochap my complain, even come and check & update me via email also don't have. This noise nuisance had tortured me for two weeks. I have had deprived insufficient sleep for a stretch of two weeks. 
I hope AVA can take action on this matter soonest, it was located at Soo Chow Rise, please walk around this whole stretch of area to check it, see how to settle this problem. 
Peace Seeker 
A.S.S. Contributor
